name: Tangle 01: Complex
description: In life, men don't always get happiness, from time to time calamities will come, big or small. Without realizing it, this calamity that comes in duration and amount is not comparable to the amount of happiness in the lives of men. Although few and short, it felt very long and endless. When disaster strikes, it really feels complicated and scary, like a puzzle falling apart, without knowing how to solve it.
